The 2023-2024 Directory Now Available for Download!

The 2023-2024 Directory of the Catholic Church in Hawaii is now available electronically only, prepared by the Hawaii Catholic Herald.

The newest release from December 29, 2023 is available in pdf form for download HERE. Please feel free to print it if you want a hard copy.
